{"id:": "/div[1]", "tag": "div", "attributes": {"type": "article", "{http://www.w3.org/XML/1998/namespace}id": "MG-1679-06_238", "resp": "mercure"}, "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]", "tag": "head", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Souhait de Socrate"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]", "tag": "bibl", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]", "tag": "title", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Mercure galant"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/text()[1]", "text": ", juin 1679 [tome 6], p. 238-242."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/text()[1]", "text": "M"}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "r"}], "attributes": {"rend": "sup"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/text()[2]", "text": " le Marquis de Chamilly, accompagné de Madame la Marquise sa Femme, est arrivé à Fribourg, dont vous sçavez qu’il est Gouverneur. La Garnison estoit sous les armes pour les recevoir, & la plus grande partie de la Cavalerie alla fort loin au devant d’eux hors des Portes de la Ville, où ils entrerent au bruit du Canon. Toutes les Troupes, & les Habitans, admirent ces deux illustres Personnes, dont les manieres, la douceur, & l’honnesteté, gagnent tous les cœurs. Ils ont esté reçeus à Brisac, & dans les autres Villes de leur route, presque avec les mesmes honneurs qu’à Fribourg. Tous les Gouverneurs en avoient donné les ordres, & ils ont tenu à gloire de traiter avec toute la distinction possible, celuy qui a si bien sçeu se distinguer luy-mesme, en soûtenant le Siege de Grave avec une valeur & une conduite qui ne recevront jamais assez de loüanges. Un mérite si extraordinaire luy a fait acquérir quantité d’Amis, quoy que ce soit l’acquisition du monde la plus difficile à faire. Ecoutez ce que Phédre nous dit là dessus d’un des plus grands Hommes de l’Antiquité. Le Fils d’un Auditeur des Comptes de Dijon luy fait parler nostre Langue."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]", "tag": "label", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Souhait "}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/lb[1]", "tag": "lb", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/text()[2]", "text": "de Socrate."}], "attributes": {"type": "head"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "SOcrate, dont le nom ne périra jamais,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Fuyant la Cour des Grands, & leurs riches Palais,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Se fit faire à l’écart, avec peu de dépense,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[4]/seg[1]", "tag": "seg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[4]/seg[1]/text()[1]", "text": "    "}], "attributes": {"type": "tab"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": "Une Maison de tres-basse apparence."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[5]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[5]/text()[1]", "text": "Un Citoyen flateur qui pres de là passoit,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[6]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[6]/seg[1]", "tag": "seg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[6]/seg[1]/text()[1]", "text": "    "}], "attributes": {"type": "tab"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[6]/seg[2]", "tag": "seg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[6]/seg[2]/text()[1]", "text": "    "}], "attributes": {"type": "tab"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[6]/text()[1]", "text": "Luy dit qu’il s’étonnoit"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[7]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[7]/text()[1]", "text": "Que des Gens comme luy, d’aussi grande importance,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[8]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[8]/text()[1]", "text": "Se vinssent renfermer en de si petits lieux."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[9]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[9]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[9]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Cet espace est petit"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[9]/text()[1]", "text": ", dit-il, "}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[9]/hi[2]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[9]/hi[2]/text()[1]", "text": "mais plût aux Dieux"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[10]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[10]/text()[1]", "text": "Pouvoir trouver encore assez d’Amis fidelles "}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[11]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[11]/seg[1]", "tag": "seg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[11]/seg[1]/text()[1]", "text": "    "}], "attributes": {"type": "tab"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[11]/seg[2]", "tag": "seg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[11]/seg[2]/text()[1]", "text": "    "}], "attributes": {"type": "tab"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[11]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[11]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Pour remplir ma Maison"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[11]/text()[1]", "text": " !"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[12]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[12]/text()[1]", "text": "Ce grand Homme, entre nous, n’avoit-il pas raison ?"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[13]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[13]/text()[1]", "text": "Il connoissoit combien les amitiez sont belles,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[14]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[14]/seg[1]", "tag": "seg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[14]/seg[1]/text()[1]", "text": "    "}], "attributes": {"type": "tab"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[14]/text()[1]", "text": "Quand la constance & la fidelité"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[15]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[15]/text()[1]", "text": "Forment ces doux liens de la societé ;"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[16]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[16]/text()[1]", "text": "Mais où chercher pour en trouver de telles ?"}]}]}]}